 So the members of the engineering and design team are now testing how to develop great experiences 

00:00:26.490 --> 00:00:31.240
 Which they receive on the planet and activate it anywhere you go to it even if in orbit, for example, 

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:35.670
 Or on the moon, or on a trip to Mars. 

