 While testing our designs on the ground, we developed a system called Astro UI and implemented this system 

00:00:41.030 --> 00:00:46.909
 Through all of our products we provide user experiences. The gloves in the additional vehicle mobility unit are very large 

00:00:46.909 --> 00:00:52.780
 So we needed to design some new icons, specifically floating action buttons 

00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:56.390
 We also used multidimensional design guidelines for this. 

