 The other challenge we face in space is gravity, or lack of gravity. Using the principles of movement 

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:10.299
 We have created a system called Fixed Point View which leads to automatic alignment 

00:01:10.299 --> 00:01:14.909
 For each of your articles, videos, and photos with the viewer no matter what your phone's status. 

